We are proud to say Five Bucks Drinkery has become a Downtown St Pete staple for over 10 years and counting. Through our big a$$ drinks, tasty food, and an atmosphere that can go from laid-back to bachelor party, its become the hang out for both locals and tourists! So whether you’re a Floridian or just flew in, we here at Five Bucks Drinkery would like to welcome you to hang out with us! And remember, what happens in Florida.. Stays in Florida!!
